fraud_detection_app/
├── app.py               # Main Flask application
├── model.py             # Model logic for fraud detection
├── requirements.txt     # Python dependencies
├── runtime.txt          # Python version for deployment
├── Procfile             # For deployment platforms like Heroku
├── model/
│   ├── xgboost_model.pkl  # Pre-trained XGBoost model
│   ├── scaler.pkl         # StandardScaler used during training
│   └── selected_features.pkl  # List of selected features
├── templates/
│   └── index.html         # HTML file for the frontend
├── static/                # Static files (CSS, JS, images)
│   └── style.css          # Optional styling for the frontend
└── _pycache_/             # Python cache files (ignore)
